---
title: Korma Paneer Skewers with Chips and Lemon Yoghurt Carrot Salad
description: Popular in Indian cuisine, paneer is also known as 'Indian cottage cheese'. Slightly squeaky in texture, it's perfect in these Korma Paneer Skewers to absorb the flavours of the korma curry paste.
